x shows up on the 3D scene, but the box is white - it should be transparent orange like all other collisions.\r\n\r\n![whitecol.gif](data/bitbucket.org/repo/jgXqbo/images/1044121385-whitecol.gif)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<ol>\n<li>Enter model editor (<code>Ctrl+M</code>)</li>\n<li>Insert a cylinder shape</li>\n<li>Double-click the shape to open the inspector</li>\n<li>In the inspector, go to the <code>Collision</code> tab</li>\n<li>Then changing the geometry to a box, for example.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The orange cylinder disappears and a box shows up on the 3D scene, but the box is white - it should be transparent orange like all other collisions.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"whitecol.gif\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/jgXqbo/images/1044121385-whitecol.gif\" /></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2018-06-01T18:17:42.663652+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2018-06-30T14:38:10.981053+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 2479}